results.name: Number of binary matrices with n distinct columns and any number of distinct nonzero rows with 4 ones in every column and rows in decreasing lexicographic order.
comment: The condition that the rows be in decreasing order is equivalent to considering nonequivalent matrices with distinct rows up to permutation of rows.
